&lt;li&gt;Advanced features are locked behind a paywall.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="3-deepcode"&gt;3. DeepCode&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DeepCode is an AI coding assistant that reviews code for bugs and security vulnerabilities. It analyzes the codebase and offers suggestions for improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
