&lt;h4 id="2-ethical-ai-and-transparency"&gt;2. &lt;strong&gt;Ethical AI and Transparency&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the rise of AI comes the responsibility to use it ethically. In 2026, businesses are prioritizing transparency and ethical considerations in their AI implementations. This includes ensuring that AI systems are free from bias and that data privacy regulations are adhered to. Companies are beginning to adopt frameworks to ensure ethical AI usage, such as the AI Ethics Guidelines from the European Commission.&lt;/p&gt;
