&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://otter.ai/?ref=AFFILIATE_ID"&gt;Otter.ai&lt;/a&gt; is an AI transcription service that transcribes spoken words into text in real time. Itâ€™s particularly useful for meetings, interviews, and lectures. For example, during a team meeting, Otter can provide an instant transcript that can be shared with all participants for reference.&lt;/p&gt;
